    "Their scores reflect a high degree of stability in interpretation and explanation, regardless of the complexity or novelty of the context.",
    "In contrast, TripoSR and GemMoE-Beta-1, while showing robust performance in familiar domains, exhibited notable variability in unfamiliar domains or when presented with ambiguous contexts.",
    "Mistral 7B's performance in consistency was influenced by its adaptive learning mechanisms.",
    "While these mechanisms offer advantages in dynamic learning environments, they occasionally resulted in less predictable interpretability in more static settings.",
    "The bar chart in Figure 3 provides a visual representation of these findings, underscoring the variability in consistency across the evaluated models."
